{"tid":2337722,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[2D]CLICKTEAM FUSION 2.5 (AVG初級教學篇)","createTime":"2020-12-23T13:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T12:04:55.000Z","uid":37475,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"504a21a2a8c1e8c0ffa0409f5d36685cbf78c6a1","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5GzRhF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5GzRhF.jpg&h=fcdc55fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nCLICKTEAM FUSION 2.5 是一個冷門的遊戲開發引擎<br />\n得罪講句,怕麻煩的話真的不要學,一路說下去就不太好憧<br />\n真的很想做完成一個遊戲才好來<br />\n發展史/安裝方法就不聊了,本篇主要講avg類遊戲的製造方法<br />\n目標大概是類似這樣的, 別跟我說其他遊戲引擎更方便<br />\n那種方便是有代價的,也不在此聊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ln3eRsi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLn3eRsi.jpg&h=33b8c891&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nAVG類型示意圖 : 限界凸記モエロクロニクル|<br />\n免費教學,慢速更新<br />\n(本教學以完整版為標準,試版可能未必有某些功能)<br />\n<a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/248170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fapp%2F248170&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=54371e78\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/app/248170</a><br />\n正版附費連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clickteam.com/clickteam-fusion-2-5-free-edition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clickteam.com%2Fclickteam-fusion-2-5-free-edition&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=26e81099\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.clickteam.com/clickteam-fusion-2-5-free-edition</a><br />\n正版免費試用<br />\n不鼓勵開心版,不過GOOGLE 如果不小心拿到了完全版不用跟我說<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUs7r3O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUs7r3O.png&h=6fec9967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各版本的功能差別"},{"pid":"8fcfe1266a6126298f7dfacaa5a73530f3e7d507","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpdiySz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpdiySz.jpg&h=c8fe8769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(1) 在 FILE 那裡可以開 NEW 的工作檔案 ,SAVE 的副檔名為 *.gam<br />\n    (舊版的MMF2 或 遊戲工廠 的gam檔案有可能打開來修改)<br />\n    <br />\n完全完成的遊戲可打包成 EXE,也可以製作該遊戲SETUP相關的東西<br />\n<br />\n(2)Application 1 ,這個是新建遊戲的名稱, 可以改名<br />\n<br />\n(3)Frame 1, 預設為 [第一關卡],名稱可改<br />\n<br />\n(4)這邊點進去可以進入建設 [第一關卡] ,當然可以加很多關卡<br />\n 但暫時是空白的<br />\n<br />\n(5)遊戲所使用的顏色模式, 建議不必要改動<br />\n(點開以前舊版遊戲檔案有機會是各種低彩模式)<br />\n<br />\n(6)WINDOWS EXE APPLICATION<br />\n一般WINDOW的EXE式遊戲<br />\n***如果你把遊戲隨便轉成其他平台<br />\n而沒有看清楚是否功能兼容<br />\n如 ANDRIOD/IOS/XNA/MAC/SWF.....<br />\n有機會出現各種故障***"},{"pid":"9824272b5b940c9195145cd592662f5db1e4fbf7","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MtDqYvx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtDqYvx.jpg&h=6c74b924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從剛才那個(4)的位置點進去<br />\n[關卡編輯器]<br />\n會出現這個畫面:<br />\n<br />\n(1)Application 1 改名成 &quot;第一個AVG遊戲&quot; (不做沒關係)<br />\n(2)Frame 1  改名成 &quot;第一個關卡&quot; (不做沒關係)<br />\n<br />\n(3)SAVE AS AVG_01.mfa (最好先加個新資料夾再存)<br />\n(資料夾最好沒有英數以外的字或空格,有機會會轉APK/SWF失敗)<br />\n(桌面/使用者/系統權限的路徑都不建議)<br />\n<br />\n(4) D:\\AVG_01  存取路徑示範<br />\n(5) AVG_01.mfa 檔案名示範<br />\n<br />\n(6) SIZE 640(點闊度) X 480 (點高度)<br />\n    (可改變,可切換模式在另一個地方設定) <br />\n   是指當遊戲視窗化是的可見部份<br />\n   即是右邊空白的長方形位置<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(7) 這是當畫面有東西需要建在可視範圍以外的時候才會用<br />\n    (建立在灰色的地方的物件/背景/敵人)<br />\n    AVG 比較少用,ACT/STG之類比較使用多<br />\n    只要比上面那個SIZE尺寸大或一樣就可以<br />\n<br />\n(8) 白色那個背景部份(可改變顏色)<br />\n    不建議更改(APK在NOX測試為無效,但真安桌機有效)<br />\n<br />\n(9)進入關卡 /離開關卡 時所使用的特效<br />\n   (內置多種,可另外下載或自製)"},{"pid":"fa490cc65ebe8fba86a1c8b90629cd978e821969","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVxjiBZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaVxjiBZ.jpg&h=644ee0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(1) 先看清楚,現在是改的視窗尺寸是&quot;關卡01&quot;<br />\n    而非所有關卡<br />\n<br />\n(2) 可視部份的闊度改為 960 PX(像數點)   <br />\n(3) 可視部份的高度改為 480 PX(像數點) <br />\n(4) 虛擬視窗部份也先設成 960 X 480 <br />\n    (不能比上面那個尺寸少 ERROR)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bW0ABqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbW0ABqR.jpg&h=258fcaee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(1) 注意***先看清楚,現在是視窗尺寸是&quot; 整個遊戲&quot; /&quot;第一個AVG遊戲&quot;*** <br />\n(2) 注意***這是PROPERTIES的第二貢***<br />\n(3) 先設成 960 X 480 <br />\n(4) STYLE ,視窗化是顯示程式名稱 / 最大化時也顯示 剔起來<br />\n(5) MENU BAR 功能列 顯示<br />\n(6) 可切換視窗解像度相關選項 , 暫時不需要先關掉<br />\n(7) 放大視窗時(ALT+ENTER)/拉動放大時<br />\n    內容跟著FIT視窗尺寸相關選項, 暫時不需要先關掉"},{"pid":"be65cad9850b7c4a6e2925a9141fdec82d76a742","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r31TocZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr31TocZ.jpg&h=22039b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.這個制是測試整個遊戲 (會自動由第一個關卡開始)<br />\n2.這個制是測試這個關卡 (只執行現在編輯的關卡)<br />\n由於暫時只有一個關卡,所以按那個都一樣<br />\n3.停止測試 /OR ALT+F4 (全畫面時)<br />\n4.第一次執行遊戲視窗<br />\n相關視窗功能選項關係看圖的箭咀,不詳細了"},{"pid":"69ec382de2b1910b730b13b26c84c515f448ca96","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssaMJfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssaMJfu.jpg&h=28f4b630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在右邊空白這裡, 按你 &quot;***滑鼠的右鍵***&quot;<br />\n出現一個功能表<br />\n選擇 : INSERT OBJECT<br />\n要開始加物件了 (OBJECT)  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNn7sJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNn7sJf.jpg&h=e5c18447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來到創建新物件視窗<br />\n(CREATE NEW OBJECT)<br />\n它左手邊雖然分了類<br />\n但未用到的我就不可能全說<br />\n先選 ACTIVE (活動物件)"},{"pid":"7f098b6b92ef012eb7040ccb4eca266279453093","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eBRDzrb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeBRDzrb.jpg&h=9b308646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.畫面中多了這個預設的 &quot;ACTIVE&quot;(物件)<br />\n在另外幾個地方會顯示這個東西給以後修改<br />\n2.點這&quot;物件&quot;鼠右鍵叫出功能表,改個易看的名字<br />\n  之後選 &quot;EDIT 編輯&quot;<br />\n準備加入你的角色圖片了"},{"pid":"e6ff2520a6f46e0504955d9b689143446a806bf7","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3fT7S9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3fT7S9.jpg&h=c9971714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出現了一個物件1號自己專用的圖像編輯視窗介面:<br />\n各種繪圖小工具<br />\n***最好不要在這裡修圖***<br />\n***其他繪圖軟件弄好才放進來***<br />\n<br />\n1.上面那些是一般可用顏色, 而這個是代表 &quot;透明的顏色&quot;<br />\n2.這是動畫的方向(面向左邊),FRAME1 就是第一格動畫<br />\n3.拉這個可以改成最多32個方向,不同動畫<br />\n4.不同情況的動畫(STOPPED:不移動的情況)<br />\n5.現在先加一張圖片,從圖片檔案中匯入"},{"pid":"76d4a62ff9b69fd9e81e3b56fcde0ce8ab8c9b31","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yPe9Gju.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyPe9Gju.jpg&h=aa40293a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.PNG 如果你不清楚它的透明色問題請不要在這裡用<br />\n2.JPG 背景比較適合<br />\n3.GIF 完整的動作才好加進來<br />\n4.PCX 如果出問題PNG 就轉成PCX吧<br />\n5.AVI/BMP/TGA 容量大, FLC/FLI 顏色數少不建議使用"},{"pid":"7aab54821e16ed50f7cdaf1f5087763ae4a59c43","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OTyoBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OTyoBi.jpg&h=bdca53c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.加入一張角色的圖片<br />\n2.按 PICK 再選取你認為是透明的單一顏色<br />\n示範的是這種綠色<br />\n3.IMPORT AS ANIMATION 是加入連續名稱的動作圖,<br />\n現在只有一張圖用不著<br />\n4.SPRITE SHEET 是一些遊戲被破解出來的圖片素材按方形來抓 FRAMES<br />\n例如 RPG製作室那些素材圖<br />\n5.CROP IMAGE 下面那些是裁切類功能<br />\n6.HOT SPOT /ACTION POINT 是程式用座標相關數值<br />\n不要現在改"},{"pid":"2c35a0aa94bb0d5242486f3409559749c07105a1","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpG0N6u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpG0N6u.jpg&h=034870c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.現在這個角色先叫做 活動物件01<br />\n2.試著測試執行<br />\n3.超出白色的部分是不會顯示出來<br />\n4.AVG通常是顯示半身,<br />\n  但畫角色圖有沒有需要畫出全身就自己決定了<br />\n5.經常記得SAVE多幾個比較安全"},{"pid":"93e8aa2a4601dfba780c33ed03c7ac958c64a889","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqZ5ZjN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqZ5ZjN.jpg&h=73b089bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然可以轉成其他平台版本,<br />\n但是是要改東改西的<br />\nAVG因為<br />\n螢幕TOUCH跟MOUSE左鍵不用改也可以用<br />\n所以比較易搞<br />\n用鍵盤或是手制就比較多野改<br />\n(要輸出成SWITCH/PS4/XBOXONE/ETC 要問官方幫手)<br />\n下次繼續講 文句系統"},{"pid":"ef49f3c25ee5510c5aca80e5f4b3cbed5a9b9f88","tid":2337722,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:18:46.000Z","msg":"Support. 樓主試下整video效果可能更好. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e444427546f1facd401d4b41c97a07eae62c7d96","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef49f3c25ee5510c5aca80e5f4b3cbed5a9b9f88","tid":2337722,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:18:46.000Z","msg":"Support. 樓主試下整video效果可能更好. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"新手睇停住睇先知係邊個位丫嘛<br />\n（介面呢D野video咁Q細隻字真係睇到盲）<br />\n我直接操作會一閃即刻消失<br />\n有測試片段會整影片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc756c7d5294bb5c5179fe884d6b49d5044d476e","tid":2337722,"uid":37475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"整片我加箭咀就變到好大工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709a395b3b13b9a783a6ea93f70b27aba3c7ebd9","tid":2337722,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T12:04:55.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外請想教<br />\n如果我有張背景圖係大過個版面<br />\n例如GAME 畫面係640x480<br />\n張bg.jpg 係 800x600<br />\n咁可以點樣自動張個bg.jpg 變成640？<br />\nThx!"}]}